description: G2 Goldfields Inc. engages in the acquisition and exploration of gold deposits in Guiana. It primarily holds 100% interests in the properties located in the Oko Aremu District and Puruni District, Guyana. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Daniel Joseph Noone B.Sc., BAPSCI (GEOL), M.B.A., MBA
